data.description: Check out this charming 2-3 bedroom home with brick paved patio; perfect for entertaining! Entering the home, you'll notice the open living room and large windows that lets the sunlight seep into the home! Spend your evenings cooking in the kitchen and then relaxing in the pine family room, which also would also work great as a 3rd bedroom. The wood built-ins would also make the room perfect for a spacious dining room; display your beautiful china or collectables to show off when friends and family come over. Head to the backyard and you'll love looking out to the trees that run right along the back of the property; what a view when fall rolls around to see the leaves turn colors! Grill out on those summer nights and sit on the patio to enjoy the sounds of the summer winds and birds chirping! Sounds like a dream to me; schedule your private showing today!
